Feature 1: User Access & Team Management

This feature ensures that only authorized users can access the app and manages team member information for assigning responsibilities.

Epic 1.1: User Authentication

Users must be able to securely access the system with their own accounts.

User Stories:

Account Creation: As a user, I want to create an account using email and password so that I can securely access the system.

Login: As a user, I want to securely log in so that I can access my meetings and tasks.

Logout: As a user, I want to log out to ensure my account remains secure on shared devices.

Epic 1.2: Team Contact Management

Users need a central repository of team members for assigning responsibilities to tasks.

User Stories:

Add Members: As a user, I want to add team members with their name and phone number so that tasks can be assigned efficiently.

View Members: As a user, I want to view a list of all team members so that I can manage contacts easily.

Edit/Delete Members: As a user, I want to edit or delete team member details to ensure contact information is accurate.